details.desc: A motor racing track located in Homestead, Florida. The track, which has several configurations, has promoted several series of racing, including NASCAR, the IndyCar Series, the WeatherTech Sportscar Championship series. Restricted is for Supers, Sports(Hotring Sabre) only, and Open wheel (Dr1).
